    <p>Link your <a href="https://joinmastodon.org">Mastodon</a> account to <a href="https://twitter.com">Twitter</a><!--
        and <a href="https://instagram.com">Instagram</a>-->. No bamboozle.</p>
    <p>
    <a target="_new" href="https://liberapay.com/hypnagogic/donate">Please consider donating to the project.
